WEBVTT

00:11:58.101 --> 00:12:00.910
New food companies
are coming up every year.

00:12:02.053 --> 00:12:03.204
And they told me,

00:12:03.228 --> 00:12:05.680
"You're not going to find
any trained workers here."

00:12:05.704 --> 00:12:07.617
I said, "It's OK, we'll teach them."

00:12:07.641 --> 00:12:10.014
We partnered with
the local community college,

00:12:10.919 --> 00:12:12.713
and while we were building the plant,

00:12:12.737 --> 00:12:16.347
we trained hundreds of hundreds of people
for advanced manufacturing.

00:12:16.371 --> 00:12:20.857
And today, our factory is one
of the largest yogurt plants in the world.

00:12:21.540 --> 00:12:24.452
(Applause)

00:12:24.476 --> 00:12:26.171
The new way of business --

00:12:27.148 --> 00:12:28.491
communities.

00:12:28.515 --> 00:12:31.283
Go search for communities
that you can be part of.